            "heading": "ROSNÆS 1-DAY RETREAT",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_zpWxmK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Escape the city and join us for a full day of slowing down in the beautiful countryside of Rosnæs, Denmark.</p><p>Together with Veatery and mindfulness guide Alex Watson, we'll spend the day moving, breathing and reconnecting through yoga, mindfulness, sound healing, sauna rituals, time in nature and nourishing seasonal food.</p><p>As a special treat, every guest will receive a curated goodie bag featuring products from our main sponsor Mantle, alongside gifts from some of our favorite partner brands.</p><p>A day to pause, recharge and connect—with yourself, nature and a like-minded community.</p>"
          }
        }
