      "blocks": {
        "row_DzFE4w": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LeonieAlma_Helen7.jpg",
            "caption": "FLOW YOGA AND SOUND",
            "heading": "helen erichsen",
            "text": "<p>Helen (@helenerichsen) is a vinyasa yoga teacher and the founder of RAVE Yoga. Combining creativity, movement and wellness, she creates immersive yoga experiences that transform any space into a place of connection and presence. Her dynamic classes blend breathwork, music and mindful movement, inviting all levels to reconnect with themselves and bring more balance into everyday life.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_qqwxUH": {
          "type": "row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_6445.jpg",
            "caption": "FOOD",
            "heading": "PHOEBE - VENN DINING",
            "text": "<p>VENN is a dining concept that unites people through the shared experience of eating. Founded by Phoebe Elsa Jordan, where a background in building community and lifelong passion for organic food forms a meeting point, a Venn diagram. VENN crafts nourishing, authentic and indulgent dining experiences where shared platters forge an immediate connection amongst diners. Rooted in a natural holistic approach, VENN is founded on the principles of organic, seasonal produce, highlighting the magic, diversity and bold flavours of the vegetable world.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_mWmkRh": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/MP_AWY_Desert_52_JPEG.png",
            "caption": "MINDFULNESS AND BREATH",
            "heading": "ALEX WATSON",
            "text": "<p>Alex creates spaces for slowing down, reconnecting, and turning inward. Through mindful practices and intentional guidance, she invites participants to step away from the noise of everyday life and cultivate a deeper connection with themselves.</p><p>Her sessions combine elements of mindfulness, breathwork, meditation, and embodied practices to support relaxation, awareness, and emotional balance. With a gentle and intuitive approach, Alex guides participants toward a greater sense of calm, clarity, and presence.</p><p>Her work is grounded in the belief that creating space within ourselves allows us to move through life with more ease and connection. By bringing attention back to the breath and the body, she offers a nurturing environment where stillness, reflection, and inner balance can naturally unfold.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_KkimNJ": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_6549.jpg",
            "caption": "FOOD AND DRINKS",
            "heading": "VEATERY",
            "text": "<p>Camille from Veatery brings a deep appreciation for food as a way to nourish, connect, and create meaningful moments together. With a passion for seasonal, plant-based cuisine, she creates dishes that are thoughtful, vibrant, and full of flavor.</p><p>Through Veatery, Camille transforms meals into experiences — celebrating fresh ingredients, beautiful presentation, and the joy of gathering around the table. Each dish is created with care, inviting guests to slow down, savor the moment, and reconnect through food.</p><p>For our retreat, Camille will prepare fresh and nourishing meals designed to support the day’s practices and leave you feeling energized, grounded, and deeply cared for.</p><p>Her work is grounded in the belief that creating space within ourselves allows us to move through life with more ease and connection. By bringing attention back to the breath and the body, she offers a nurturing environment where stillness, reflection, and inner balance can naturally unfold.</p>",
            "button_label": "Button label",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
